infos.title: How To Play This Run Game
infos.text: Welcome to Run Forrest Run, the official game of Forrest Gump! Enjoy endless running in this amazing adventure. Have fun on the run, dashing and beating every level with Forrest Gump in this great runner game!
infos.text_two: Run as Forrest Gump through the levels, collecting coins and dashing in the jungle, enjoy playing this game as the star of an award-winning Paramount Pictures film!

infos.title: Unlimited Running
infos.text: Run unlimited in the jungle of Vietnam. Dash fast, rush to overcome levels, unlock new scenarios and characters. Try running as fast as possible in this endless running adventure game without wifi (offline game).
infos.text_two: While running, get boosters & power ups to run unlimited time in all the scenarios and have a lot of fun. A wild race is waiting: run, jump and dodge! rush and dash through a fusion of arcade and action game, enjoy some casual fun for everyone and running games.
